reviewText: Amazing family...great music.  Will purchase more of their DVD's and CD's.  Very uplifting.
The Collingsworth Family is always a blessing to your heart.
Love this dvd not one that I don't love by them
Great variety of music from this extremely talented family.  Bought these to give as gifts. Wish there was a CD of this music.
Beatiful family harmony and a great selection of gospel and secular songs.

We were there when they recorded this DVD and pre-ordered it at that time.  It was fantastic in person and for some reason it seemed even better when we watched the DVD.  They are such a talented family!  If you love good Christian music you will really enjoy this concert.  All ages will enjoy this.
I really enjoyed the music. I have already watched it twice. Glad I bought it.
Just love the collingsworth family. Love to see and hear them perform
Another great video by the Collingsworth Family. I bought it for a senior friend who loves these folks and he has given me great reports on this latest production
They are incredible!  This is an excellent project.
The whole family ages 2-55 love this!
I think i have every CD they've made . . + a few DVDs!
Great family harmony. Great conservative Christian music.

My family thoroughly enjoyed this DVD.  We are fans of the Collingsworth Family and are pleased to have this DVD available whenever we wish to listen and view their excellent presentation.  We found the personal comments added to the musical presentation to be enjoyable as well.
Had some skips in the cd
